snippet.textDisplay:
Wow. You all must use the same source Dreamcast Guy gets his PS5 info from. I usually have no issue with rumor videos cause after all, it's just rumors. But this is an entirely new level of BS.

So now we wait till summer to see if you are correct in your assumptions, or if Nintendo outright lies to the public. Remember, Nintendo's past denials have been the standard, "We can't comment on rumors", PR comment. With the Lite, Nintendo only said they didn't have any plans to announce any new hardware at E3'19. And indeed that was the case as it was revealed AFTER E3. No deception in what they've said at all.

When it comes to rumored hardware announcements, you have to pay attention to the wording of them. Nintendo has officially stated no new hardware in 2020 and I'm holding them to that.

A 2021 or later Switch hardware update would mess with Sony and Microsoft quite a bit. 🙂
